      "id": "legend_txt",
      "x": 82,
      "y": 1082,
      "width": 1380,
      "height": 18,
      "text": "gold = the gate that decides      cyan = inputs, the worker, the tools it runs      green = a thread is done, durably recorded      dashed = it loops / recovers on its own",
